		<c>The tag (or MAC) GENERATED BY THE CAVS by using the DKM to MAC the Message with the specified method </c>
		<c>value</c>
		<c>Yes</c>
		<c/><c/><c/><c/>

		<c>nonceEphem</c>
		<c>nonceEphem ONLY USED BY C(1,2) and C(0,2) schemes with KC. nonce to be used in the MacData field</c>
		<c>value</c>
		<c>Yes</c>
		<c/><c/><c/><c/>

		<c>nonceDKMIUT</c>
